Sequence:


////////////////////////////////////////
// CATEGORY: LOCATION (LOCAL)
// TYPE:     CREATED  (CRIADO)
// SUBTYPE:  ROAD     (ESTRADA)
////////////////////////////////////////

// Example: Ponte Salgueiro Maia
// Example: Ponte D. Henrique
1> NOUN[location=+,road=+] @= ?[SEM-Lpath2], (prep, (art)), ?[noun,SEM-Hpeople].

1> NOUN[location=+,road=+] @= ?[SEM-Lpath2], (prep, (art)), ?+[noun,proper].
